tool_description: Summarize YouTube videos in any language and length with GPT-4 or GPT-3.5-Turbo. No OpenAI API Key required. Use any valid YouTube URL.
name: YouTube Summary Multilanguage
title: YouTube Summary Multilanguage

api_list.name: OK quality YouTube Summary (gpt-3.5-turbo)
api_list.description: OK quality summary made by gpt-3.5-turbo OpenAI model for videos of any length.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://youtube-summary-multilanguage.p.rapidapi.com/summarize/long/gpt-3.5-turbo"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "youtube-summary-multilanguage.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
